Share your skills and pick up some new ones at our weekly hack sessions!

Join us at the Urbana-Champaign Independent Media Center, 202 S. Broadway Ave., Urbana, from 7 to 9 PM.

This is a weekly Py-CU event for people to work on projects, seek assistance on projects, socialize, plan, and generally enjoy being around people who like to code, too. Individuals of all levels of programming experience are encouraged to come.

Update: what we talked about and worked on

  • CU Fab Lab’s DustDuino
  • WordPress, Twitter Bootstrap, Amazon Web Services
  • and more!
